So beautiful and great helpful staff. Love this place

What can I say other than I'm not really fond of this store I prefer the Idlewild location or the Matthew's location. The last two times I've come to the store I really haven't had a great experience. It seems like the store employees are either a unhappy with their job or just don't want to be there. I have tried talking to several of the people and they act like I was bothering when I was asking something for my purchase. And I ordered three small pink drinks from my daughter and her two cousins and I ordered me a large caramel caramel frappe with extra Carmel. Well the three pink drinks were made right away and I had to wait like 5 to 10 minutes for my caramel frappe I just thought it was a little odd that those drinks at there and for almost ten minutes while I had to wait for my other drink. I understand the stores new and they probably got a lot of things to work on but I'm not going to come back here I don't feel welcome
Love them...

Brand new but had Zero available plugs to connect your laptop and do some work while drinking and eating starbucks products.  Will have to go to alternate locations that give a reason to stay and buy more drinks/food.
I do not agreed to the bathrooms being share man with women. I believe it should be separated. Please separate the bathrooms women or man thank you.
Not very friendly
Unbelievably slow drive thru

So I don't go to starbucks...I know..! But today I ordered something that was recommended to me. I definitely ordered it wrong and they were so kind to fix it for me the correct way!! I'm a coffee ordering amateur!
This is a new location and the service is typically decent but expect to wait longer than normal. They're good people, just short-staffed. I'm sure they're working on it.
there is a particular person there that throws their food like they are giving a dog a treat.  I do not want to engage in a very out spoken argument. I will avoid this particular Starbucks.
I loved it but there’s no outlets!
The barista at the window rushed us to order, "we gotta hurry "...and made several remarks and annoyed faces when we asked to reload card.

El lugar es amplio, tiene un buen espacio de estacionamiento, hay lugar tanto dentro como mesas afuera para disfrutar lo malo que estaban sucias las mesas llenas de polvo y con marcas de los vasos de café, atención regularmente bien
I love this location. However, a double lane would've been so much better for this location since it's on one of the main highway
New Starbucks for the area, mobile order was quick and I was greeted by everyone when I walked in. Keep up the great work.

Nice Starbucks right when you're leaving Charlotte. Seems to be pretty newly constructed. It was the middle of the afternoon, but I went in and got my coffee quickly with no wait whatsoever. Interior was nice and clean.
Great service at the drive thru. The person was very polite.
The person at the drive thru just now was a rockstar! Very polite and personable
Nice new spot
New favorite
Quiet, new store, employees were nice.

They handed me a scalding hot cup of coffee filled to the brim at the drive through window. The lid would not stay on the cup. Literally dripping on my hand as she handed it to me. I gave it right back and pointed out how dangerous that could be for a driver like myself. Tidepod eater says it’s not her fault because she didn’t make the cup.

The woman at drive thru was great. Quick question starbucks prifitted 22 billion last year for 2022( i just looked it up) how is it you made that much money but employees at the drive thru are asking for tips on credit reader. If you think your employees should get paid more why dont you pay them??? And to all the employees that might read this start a union already. You work for a 22 billion dollar profit corporation. You deserve to live comfortable too, START A UNION.

My friends and I are in town from Pennsylvania!  The location is very convenient!   we were greeted by Shiloh who took our orders and the service was great!!!  Shiloh was super super friendly and personable!!!!! The establishment was clean, neat and our drinks were prepared deliciously. We’ll be returning every morning for the remainder of our trip :).
Muy buena sucursal,Aquí mi café si sabe a café no como en otras sucursales de starbucks

The cup was less than half full. We realized it once we returned home. No phone number on the website or receipt so we came here. I hope someone reaches back out. Almost $6.00 for maybe 4 oz of coffee.
